\frac{\pi}{\sin (\pi z)}=\sum_{n=-\infty}^\infty (-1)^n \frac{1}{z-n},
\sec(z)=\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n(2n-1)\pi}{z^2-(n-1/2)^2\pi^2}?
